{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9a0694cce","title":"对政务院关于设置文史研究馆的决定草案的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"387fc1c5e1","index":0,"year":1952,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"e9a0694cce"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"7e148c8144","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓，指邓小平，当时任政务院副总理。"},{"id":"8ac6e9a0e5","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指送审的政务院关于设置文史研究馆的决定（草案）。决定草案说：中央人民政府自1951年7月成立文史研究馆，吸收了不少社会凤有声望的文人着宿。华东、中南某些地区也设有类似组织，安置了一部分年老贫困的知识分子。估计全国各省、市有不少此类年老失业的知识分子需要照顾，因此决定：全国各省及中央或大行政区的直属市均设置文史研究馆（大区、专、县及省属市不必设立），如某些省、市原已成立类似机构的，必要时可更换名称，不必重复设立。"},{"id":"f7a7873da5","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东加写的一句话是：“某些省市无设立此项机构之需要者，亦不必设立。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"313a47f7ab","type":"title","text":"对政务院关于设置文史研究馆的决定草案的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce"},{"id":"7e148c8144","type":"paragraph","text":"刘阅，退邓办。同意这个决定。加了一句”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce"},{"id":"8ac6e9a0e5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce"},{"id":"f7a7873da5","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十八日[I]刘，指刘少奇。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce"}],"page":{"id":"01c311a0c4","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e9a0694cce","start":201,"end":201}}}},"__N_SSG":true}